column5: This was made by a guy from Quebec with a landlocked Atlantic salmon he caught in Lake Champlain, Vermont.  I thought it was an instructional video at first, until I sprayed my coffee all over the screen from laughing so hard.  Worth the one minute to watch!  <iframe width="853" height="480" src="http://www.youtube.com/embed/uvCNdMiOb7A" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe>
